With less than 24 hours to the budget reading Kenyans will be waiting with bated breath on just how the government will finance the 3.6 trillion-shilling budget. Ktn&rsquo;s Aby Agina looks at what to expect in the budget and why it will be a tough balancing act for the National Treasury Cabinet Secretary Amb. Ukur Yattani has today faced a setback after the budgets and appropriations committee made some sweeping changes in the budget.